<div class="content">
  <div class="privacy-policy" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1rem 0 3rem;">
    <h2 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Beanstalk &mdash; Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="open-sans light" style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Last updated: March 12, 2026</p>

    <p>TomKat Creative (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo;, or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) operates the Beanstalk mobile application (the &ldquo;App&rdquo;). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the App.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>When you use Beanstalk, we may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Email address and password used to sign in to your account. Accounts are created by authorized administrators, not through self-registration.</li>
      <li><strong>Profile information:</strong> Your name and role within your organization, as provided by your administrator.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> General information about how you interact with the App, such as device type, operating system version, and app version.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li>Authenticate your identity and provide access to the App</li>
      <li>Deliver the services and features of the App</li>
      <li>Maintain and improve the App&rsquo;s performance and reliability</li>
      <li>Communicate important updates about the service</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">3. Third-Party Services</h3>
    <p>Beanstalk uses the following third-party services to operate:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li><strong>Google Firebase:</strong> For authentication, data storage, and app infrastructure. Firebase&rsquo;s privacy policy is available at <a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">firebase.google.com/support/privacy</a>.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">4. Data Storage and Security</h3>
    <p>Your data is stored securely using Google Firebase infrastructure. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. All data is encrypted in transit using TLS and encrypted at rest.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">5. Data Retention</h3>
    <p>We retain your personal information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you with the App&rsquo;s services. If your account is deactivated by an administrator, we will retain your data only as long as necessary to fulfill our legal obligations.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">6. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h3>
    <p>Beanstalk is a business application designed for use by adults. The App is not directed at children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us so we can promptly delete it.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">7. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">8. Changes to This Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by updating the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date at the top of this page. Your continued use of the App after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h3 class="open-sans bold" style="color: #007876; margin-top: 1.5rem;">9. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>TomKat Creative<br>
    Email: <a href="mailto:tomkatcreative@gmail.com">tomkatcreative@gmail.com</a></p>
